headline: AIG Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates, Up Y/Y on Solid Underwriting
summary: American International posts a 51% EPS surge in Q4, beating estimates as underwriting strength offsets weaker premiums and investment income pressures.

headline: Global Insurer AIG Held At Bay For Now Despite A-Level Credit Rating
